snippet.title: SHE RUINED HIS CAREER! Why I think Johnny Depp Is Innocent-Makeup Monday
snippet.description:
Welcome back to Makeup Mondays! Today we are going through the evidence between Johnny Depp and Ex-wife Amber Heard as I explain why I truly believe Johnny Depp was the victim of domestic abuse in this relationship. This video is purely for entertainment purposes and I was neither witness to the actual events accused or the trial recently in London. Please fact check all information for yourselves. Check out the accounts linked in the closing of this video for more information on this topic! Also be sure to check out my social media and put in recommendations for the next Makeup Monday.
